[ProMED-mail thanks Dr Berger for providing information on the 3 additional human pathogenic arenaviruses in the Americas and references to them. - Mod.TY]

[There is a 7th deadly human pathogenic arenavirus in the Americas, Chapare virus in Bolivia, see the 2008 ProMED archive below. - Mod.JW]
